Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT DISTINCT L.* FROM [Logement] AS L JOIN [Avis] AS A ON L.[idLogement] = A.[idLogement] WHERE (SELECT AVG([note]) FROM Avis WHERE Avis.idLogement = L.IdLogement)>(SELECT AVG([note]) FROM [Avis])

Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT [idReservation], [dateDebut], [dateFin], L.[pays] FROM [Reservation] AS R JOIN [Logement] as L ON R.[idLogement] = L.[idLogement]

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: SELECT * FROM [Logement] WHERE [DateCreation] BETWEEN CONVERT(DATETIME,DATEDIFF(DAY,30,GETDATE())) AND GETDATE()

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: BEGIN SELECT L.*, R.[dateDebut], R.[dateFin] FROM [Logement] AS L JOIN [Reservation] AS R ON R.[idLogement] = L.[idLogement] JOIN [Annulation] AS A ON A.[idReservation] = R.[IdReservation] WHERE R.[dateDebut] >= GETDATE() AND A.[dateAnnulation] IS NULL AND R.[idClient] = @id_client END
